    public class AdminConsoleService
extends StandardMBean
implements AdminConsoleServiceMBean
    This class provides convenience methods for interacting with OSGi/Felix ConfigurationAdmin services.

        public boolean updateGuestClaimsProfile(String pid,
                                        Map<String,Object> configurationTable)
                                 throws IOException
        Description copied from interface: AdminConsoleServiceMBean
        Interceptor method for special handling of guest claims profile data.
        Specified by:
        updateGuestClaimsProfile in interface AdminConsoleServiceMBean
        Parameters:
        pid - the persistent identifier of the configuration
        configurationTable - the table of properties
        Throws:
        IOException - if the operation fails AdminConsoleServiceMBean.update(String, Map).
        See Also:
        for the generic version of this method; this method acts as an interceptor to handle the special case where processing specific to guest claims occurs before passing the configuration data to {@link #update(String, Map)} for persistence in OSGi's configuration admin.
